sequenceDiagram
    Title: 0.4: Nova Nota

    loop POST Method
        browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa
        server-->browser: HTML
        browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
        server-->browser: main.css
        browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.js
        server-->browser: main.js

        Nota browser: O browser começa a executar o código JS que faz um pedido de dados JSON através do servidor

        browser->server: HTTP GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
        server-->browser: [{ content: "Top G", date: "2023-09-22" }, ...]

        Nota browser: O browser executa o evento princiapl que apresenta as notas no ecrã

        browser->server: HTTP POST {note: 'Your inputting content.'}

        Nota browser: A página é atualizada
    end
